- Create a role with s3 full acccess

- attach the role to the ec2 instance

- create a new bucket from the command line
  - aws s3 mb s3://holyswagger-presigned-fidelis

- upload a new file to the bucket

- To give temporary access to objects in the s3 bucket we can create presigned url to access the object

- aws s3 presign s3://holyswagger-presigned-fidelis/hello.txt --expires-in 300
